Algorithm-ConvexHull
====================

Calculates the convex hull of a set of points

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module will use the module Sort::Key::Radix when installed.

